item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

[quote=“1 sec u k0ed, post:4, topic:268594”]i had ur source befor.Go into Client.java and anything that says like…reapage…or the reaper change that to ur server name or ur in-game name :).[/quote]No.

[quote=“MoparScapeHelp, post:5, topic:268594”]Search the original owner’s name on client.java and change that to your name[/quote]No.

Look at some Sun Java tutorials and learn how the private server works. If you want to have an original server than you going to have to learn to add and change packets, modify skills add minigames, quests or something fun that will drive players to play your server.

Try not to stick everything in client.java. Try create other handlers and instance them from your server.java.
